OL,3,CLeo Scienza: Southampton's play-off
OL,4,Cexpulsion over 'Spygate' is
OL,5,C'heartbreaking'
OL,7,FSouthampton winger Leo Scienza
OL,8,Fadmitted the club's expulsion from the
OL,9,FChampionship play-offs for spying
OL,10,Foffences was "heartbreaking" and that
OL,11,Fthe club's fans "definitely deserved
OL,12,Fbetter".
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough will play Hull in
OL,15,FSaturday's final at Wembley after
OL,16,FSaints lost their appeal against
OL,17,Fsanctions imposed for 'Spygate'.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@\O]sD@QOUtD@GO]
