OL,3,CLeo Scienza: Southampton's play-off
OL,4,Cexpulsion over 'Spygate' is
OL,5,C'heartbreaking'
OL,7,FSouthampton admitted three spying
OL,8,Fcharges, including observing a Boro
OL,9,Ftraining session ahead of winning 2-1
OL,10,Fon aggregate in the play-off semi-
OL,11,Ffinals.
OL,13,FThe Hampshire club were also docked
OL,14,Ffour points for next season.
OL,16,FSaints player of the year Scienza
OL,17,Fposted on Instagram: "Disappointment,
OL,18,Fanger, sadness...It's difficult to
OL,19,Ffind the right words for what we're
OL,20,Fall feeling right now.
OL,26,@yD@VOU
