OL,3,CLeo Scienza: Southampton's play-off
OL,4,Cexpulsion over 'Spygate' is
OL,5,C'heartbreaking'
OL,7,FSaints' appeal was dismissed on
OL,8,FWednesday, denying them the chance of
OL,9,Fa shot at promotion to the Premier
OL,10,FLeague worth an estimated #200million
OL,11,Fat a minimum.
OL,13,F"I feel sorry for every football fan,
OL,14,Fas well as the players and supporters
OL,15,Fof Hull and Boro, who were caught up
OL,16,Fin all of this chaos too," Brazilian
OL,17,FScienza, who registered seven goals
OL,18,Fand 10 assists in 44 appearances,
OL,19,Fadded.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
