PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779447783
OL,3,CLeo Scienza: Southampton's play-off
OL,4,Cexpulsion over 'Spygate' is
OL,5,C'heartbreaking'
OL,7,F"We gave everything for this dream.
OL,8,FDay after day, sacrifice after
OL,9,Fsacrifice, always believing we could
OL,10,Fbring this club back to where it
OL,11,Fbelongs.
OL,13,F"For me, the dream of playing in the
OL,14,FPremier League was something I fought
OL,15,Ffor with everything I had. That's why
OL,16,Fthis pain cuts so deep.
OL,18,F"The hardest part is knowing how much
OL,19,Four fans deserved this moment. You
OL,20,Fstood behind us all season with
OL,21,Fincredible passion, loyalty and belief.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
