PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779447783
OL,3,CLeo Scienza: Southampton's play-off
OL,4,Cexpulsion over 'Spygate' is
OL,5,C'heartbreaking'
OL,7,F"Even in the toughest moments, you
OL,8,Fcarried us forward.
OL,10,F"Thank you for staying with us through
OL,11,Feverything, you definitely deserved
OL,12,Fbetter."
OL,14,FSouthampton chief executive Phil
OL,15,FParsons described the punishment as
OL,16,F"manifestly disproportionate" to any
OL,17,Fother sanction handed down in the
OL,18,Fhistory of the English game.
OL,20,FSaints had sold more than 37,000
OL,21,Ftickets for the play-off final.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@HO]xD@AOUxD@]O]
